// Quake variables
//
//      args[0]     Intensity on richter scale (2..9)
//      args[1]     Duration in tics
//      args[2]     Radius for damage
//      args[3]     Radius for tremor
//      args[4]     TID of map thing for focus of quake
//
//===========================================================================

